import React from 'react';
import { Container, Formula, Header, NumPad, Key, Title } from './style';

const Calculator: React.FC = () => {
	return (
		<Container>
			<Header>
				<Title></Title>
				<Formula>1.5^10+5</Formula>
			</Header>
			<NumPad>
				<Key style={{color: 'var(--text-secundary)'}}>C</Key>
				<Key>±</Key>
				<Key>%</Key>
				<Key>÷</Key>
				<Key>7</Key>
				<Key>8</Key>
				<Key>9</Key>
				<Key>4</Key>
				<Key>5</Key>
				<Key>6</Key>
				<Key>1</Key>
				<Key>2</Key>
				<Key>3</Key>
				<Key>0</Key>
				<Key>.</Key>
				<Key>=</Key>
			</NumPad>
		</Container>
	);
};

export default Calculator;
